---------------- CONTROL COMMANDS ---------------  P  page status                  U   Underline  N  name the last error          O   Overline  V  View/hide character mods     Y   Superscript  F  Format command display       K   Subscript  ^  Upper case lock              B   Boldface  A  Assistance  W  delete word  D  delete single character  X  delete line  R  set a tab  I  move to tab  G  insert ghost hyphen  E  Go to Programmers mode